---
title: Korean Glazed Beef Strips with Sesame Pear Slaw & Crispy Shallots
description: How to improve on your everyday beef strips? Toss them in some Korean stir-fry sauce, of course! It adds loads of flavour and
that saucy touch that makes every mouthful a delight. The additioon of creamy slaw and crispy shallots are just the ticket to seal
the deal.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
